docs.lead_paragraph: MARINE HOSPITAL.--On the 19th ult., in the House of Representatives, the Civil and Diplomatic Appropriation hill being under consideration, Mr. BROWN, of Alississippi, moved to amend by inserting the following appropriation for Marine Hospitals: Cleveland, Ohio, $15,000; Pittsburg, Penn., $5,000 ; St. Louis, Mo., $20,000; Louisville, Ky., $3,000; Paducah, Ky., $3,000; Napolcon, Ark., $4,000; Natchez, Miss., $4,000;--to be expended in finishing, repairing, heating and fencing the buildings.
